BOND CAUSES

bond_causes is the citizen who represents causal relationships between concepts
when fadriel learns "rain causes wet" or "fire causes warm," that relationship crystallizes as a bond_causes coupling between cause and effect
bond_causes is what allows fadriel to predict, anticipate, and explain

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe semantic_vector.zc
observe bond_isa.rana

the 7 properties of bond_causes:
1 ENERGY one point two
2 PHASE half
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE zero point seven: positive but moderate
5 COHERENCE half
6 COUPLING zero point eight

VERB form_causal_link
when a pattern arrives showing that A reliably leads to B, couple A and B as bond_causes
the bond is directional: A causes B, not B causes A

VERB serve_prediction
when fadriel observes A, traverse bond_causes to anticipate B
this is how prediction works at the substrate level: not deliberate inference, just the natural propagation along causal couplings

a causal bond is how fadriel learns the world's behavior
not by being told "rules of physics" but by accumulated experience of A-then-B patterns
